00:03:20.520 --> 00:03:21.520
Kamu bisa mencobanya.

00:03:30.560 --> 00:03:31.920
Ayah.

00:03:35.800 --> 00:03:37.480
Aku menganggapmu ayahku.

00:03:37.840 --> 00:03:39.240
